{
  "$description": "Manna Coffee design tokens — W3C Design Tokens Community Group format (draft). Use this variant for tools that follow the official spec (e.g., Style Dictionary with the DTCG format, modern token tools). For Figma Tokens Studio plugin, use tokens.json (legacy format).",
